quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,94,"Kandi ntabwo twohereza umuhanuzi mu mudugudu uwo ari wo wose (ngo ahinyurwe), maze ngo tubure guhanisha abawutuye ibizazane no guhagarika umutima n’indwara z’ibyorezo kugira ngo bicishe bugufi (banicuze kuri Allah)"
  7,95,"Nuko imibereho mibi yabo tuyihindura myiza, kugeza ubwo biyongereye baranakungahara, maze baravuga bati “(Ibi ni na ko byagendaga kuva kera kuko) abakurambere bacu bagerwagaho n’ibizazane ndetse n’ibyiza (bidatewe no guhakana).” Nuko tubagwa gitumo (tubahana) batabizi"
  7,96,"Kandi n’iyo abatuye imidugudu baza kwemera bakanatinya (Allah), mu by’ukuri twari kubafungurira imigisha iturutse mu kirere no mu isi, ariko barahakanye; nuko tubahanira ibyo bakoraga"
  7,97,"Ese abatuye imidugudu bibwira ko batekanye, ko nta gihano cyacu cyabageraho nijoro baryamye"
  7,98,"Cyangwa abatuye imidugudu bibwira ko batekanye, ko nta gihano cyacu cyabageraho ku gasusuruko bahugiye mu kwishimisha (mu by’isi)"
  7,99,"Ese bibwira ko batekanye, badashobora kugerwaho n’ibihano bya Allah? Nta bantu bakwibwira ko badashobora kugerwaho n’ibihano bya Allah uretse abanyagihombo"